Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Holy]{/}{/}{nl}增加HP、SP 恢復能力。
Effect: HP恢復增加100{nl}SP恢復增加100{nl}冷卻時間減少5秒
Name: 增加HP、SP恢復力
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Name: 高級守護
SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Strike] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}拿著盾牌推著敵人跑。鄰近的敵人會被盾牌撞倒。盾牌衝鋒中格擋和物理防禦力增加。{nl}{#00113F}套用疾奔BUFF時，被攻擊的敵人移動速度會減慢。{/}
Effect: 每0.5秒技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#%{nl}格擋、物理防禦力增加 #{CaptionRatio}#%{nl}最大持續時間5秒{nl}消耗耐力
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Rodelero11\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Rodelero11\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Cataphract11\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Cataphract11\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]
Name: 突擊
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\") == \"YES\") {", "", "    if (TryGetProp(skill, \"EnableCompanion\") == \"YES\"  &&  TryGetProp(skill, \"ValueType\") == \"Attack\") {", "", "        if (IsServerSection() == 1) {", "            var acrobaticBuff = GetBuffByName(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\")", "            var acrobaticBuffLevel = GetBuffArg(acrobaticBuff)", "            var acrobaticAddSPRate = acrobaticBuffLevel * 0.05", "            value = value *(1 + acrobaticAddSPRate)", "            SetExProp(acrobaticBuff, \"ACROBATICMOUNT_SPENDSP\", Math.floor(value));", "        } else {", "            var acrobaticBuff = GET_BUFF_BY_NAME_C(\"AcrobaticMount_Buff\");", "            var acrobaticBuffLevel = acrobaticBuff.arg1;", "            var acrobaticAddSPRate = acrobaticBuffLevel * 0.05", "            value = value *(1 + acrobaticAddSPRate)", "        }", "", "    }", "", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var value = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "value = value - (skill.Level * 1000);", "return value"]

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical] - [Piercing]{/}{/}{nl}向前方投擲長槍，攻擊範圍內的多數敵人。遭受攻擊的敵人暫時會對近距離物理屬性攻擊脆弱，
Effect: 技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#%{nl}Debuff 持續時間10秒
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Dragoon5\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Dragoon5\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]
Name: 穿刺之矛
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "var addValue = 1", "var pcLevel = TryGetProp(pc, \"Lv\", 1)", "var mnaRate = TryGetProp(pc, \"MNA\", 1)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"DragoonHelmet_Buff\") == \"YES\") {", "    addValue = 2", "    addValue = addValue - Math.min(0.5, mnaRate / pcLevel)", "    value = Math.floor(value * addValue)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"DragoonHelmet_Abil_Buff\") == \"YES\") {", "    addValue = 1.5", "    addValue = addValue - Math.min(0.5, mnaRate / pcLevel)", "    value = Math.floor(value * addValue)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Name: 戰鬥命令
SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (IsServerSection(owner) == 1) {", "    var list, cnt = GetPartyMemberList(owner, PARTY_NORMAL, 0);", "", "    if (cnt > 1) {", "        var abilCoolDownRatio = 1;", "        for (var i = 1;  cnt - 1 ;) {", "            abilCoolDownRatio = abilCoolDownRatio - 0.1;", "        }", "", "", "        if (abilCoolDownRatio < 0.6) {", "            abilCoolDownRatio = 0.6;", "        }", "", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * abilCoolDownRatio;", "    }", "", "} else {", "    var list = session.party.GetPartyMemberList(PARTY_NORMAL);", "", "    if (list != null) {", "        var cnt = list.Count();", "", "        if (cnt > 1) {", "            var myObj = session.party.GetMyPartyObj(PARTY_NORMAL)", "            var myMapID = myObj.GetMapID()", "            var myChannelInfo = session.loginInfo.GetChannel();", "            var loginCount = 0;", "            for (var i = 0 ;  cnt - 1 ;) {", "                var partyMemberInfo = list.Element(i);", "", "                if (partyMemberInfo.GetMapID() == myMapID  &&  partyMemberInfo.GetChannel() == myChannelInfo) {", "                    loginCount = loginCount + 1;", "                }", "", "            }", "", "            var abilCoolDownRatio = 1;", "", "            if (loginCount > 1) {", "                for (var i = 1;  loginCount - 1 ;) {", "                    abilCoolDownRatio = abilCoolDownRatio - 0.1;", "                }", "", "            }", "", "", "            if (abilCoolDownRatio < 0.6) {", "                abilCoolDownRatio = 0.6;", "            }", "", "            basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * abilCoolDownRatio;", "        }", "", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"Bunshin_Debuff\") == \"YES\") {", "    var bunshinBuff = null", "    var bunsinCount = null", "", "    if (IsServerObj(pc) == 1) {", "        bunshinBuff = GetBuffByName(pc, \"Bunshin_Debuff\")", "        bunsinCount = GetBuffArg(bunshinBuff)", "    } else {", "        var handle = session.GetMyHandle();", "        bunshinBuff = info.GetBuff(handle, 3049)", "        bunsinCount = bunshinBuff.arg1", "    }", "", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + (bunsinCount * 2000 + (basicCoolDown * (bunsinCount * 0.1)))", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Buff] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}插上勝利的旗幟，讓我軍的士氣提升，造成敵人的士氣低下。我軍暴擊率會增加，在PVP時受到的傷害會減少。敵人暴擊抵抗會減少。{nl}騎馬狀態下使用飄揚的旗幟，會為我軍套用PVP時遭受傷害減少10%的效果。
Effect: 持續時間 15秒{nl}我軍暴擊發生增加 #{CaptionRatio}#% {nl}PVP時，遭受傷害減少 #{CaptionRatio2}#% {nl}敵暴擊抵抗減少 #{CaptionRatio}#%
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Templar7\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Templar7\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = skill.Level * 8", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return value"]
Name: 飄揚的旗幟

Name: 粉碎一擊
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\") == \"YES\") {", "", "    if (TryGetProp(skill, \"EnableCompanion\") == \"YES\"  &&  TryGetProp(skill, \"ValueType\") == \"Attack\") {", "", "        if (IsServerSection() == 1) {", "            var acrobaticBuff = GetBuffByName(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\")", "            var acrobaticBuffLevel = GetBuffArg(acrobaticBuff)", "            var acrobaticAddSPRate = acrobaticBuffLevel * 0.05", "            value = value *(1 + acrobaticAddSPRate)", "            SetExProp(acrobaticBuff, \"ACROBATICMOUNT_SPENDSP\", Math.floor(value));", "        } else {", "            var acrobaticBuff = GET_BUFF_BY_NAME_C(\"AcrobaticMount_Buff\");", "            var acrobaticBuffLevel = acrobaticBuff.arg1;", "            var acrobaticAddSPRate = acrobaticBuffLevel * 0.05", "            value = value *(1 + acrobaticAddSPRate)", "        }", "", "    }", "", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Physical] - [Piercing]{/}{/}{nl}360度旋轉，攻擊周圍敵人，在攻擊的途中施展者不會受到攻擊造成的傷害，遭到攻擊的敵人會在原地倒下。攻擊敵人時，自身的暴擊率會增加。
Effect: 技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#% x 4次{nl}廣域攻擊比率 #{SkillSR}#{nl}暴擊發生增加20%
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Matador5\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Matador5\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\") == \"YES\") {", "", "    if (TryGetProp(skill, \"EnableCompanion\") == \"YES\"  &&  TryGetProp(skill, \"ValueType\") == \"Attack\") {", "", "        if (IsServerSection() == 1) {", "            var acrobaticBuff = GetBuffByName(pc, \"AcrobaticMount_Buff\")", "            var acrobaticBuffLevel = GetBuffArg(acrobaticBuff)", "            var acrobaticAddSPRate = acrobaticBuffLevel * 0.05", "            value = value *(1 + acrobaticAddSPRate)", "            SetExProp(acrobaticBuff, \"ACROBATICMOUNT_SPENDSP\", Math.floor(value));", "        } else {", "            var acrobaticBuff = GET_BUFF_BY_NAME_C(\"AcrobaticMount_Buff\");", "            var acrobaticBuffLevel = acrobaticBuff.arg1;", "            var acrobaticAddSPRate = acrobaticBuffLevel * 0.05", "            value = value *(1 + acrobaticAddSPRate)", "        }", "", "    }", "", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Strike] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}連續攻擊敵人上半身，讓敵人陷入昏厥狀態。{nl}{#00113F}狂怒Buff套用時，破顱斬的攻擊範圍會變大，昏厥的持續時間變更為4秒。{/}
Effect: 技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#% x 2次{nl}廣域攻擊比率 #{SkillSR}#
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Hackapell15\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Hackapell15\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (basicCoolDown < skill.MinCoolDown) {", "    return skill.MinCoolDown;", "}", "", "return basicCoolDown;"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Magic] - [Soul]{/}{/}{nl}強化指定範圍的重力，讓敵人受到炎屬性傷害，範圍內的空中型敵人會變更為地上型，生成時會解除周圍的浮空魔法陣。對變異型怪物的傷害增加 50%。
Effect: 每0.5秒技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#%{nl}持續時間5秒
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Psychokino21\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Psychokino21\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]
Name: 強力重力
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Magic] - [Lightning]{/}{/}{nl}發射電氣鎖鍊連續攻擊前方的敵人們。{nl}{#00113F}在呼風喚雨符範圍內使用電擊時，可以套用的對象數會增加為2倍。{/}
Name: 電擊
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (basicCoolDown < skill.MinCoolDown) {", "    return skill.MinCoolDown;", "}", "", "return basicCoolDown;"]
Description: {#993399}{ol}[Magic] - [Earth]{/}{/}{nl}召喚吸血蝙蝠飛向敵人，造成傷害。被攻擊的敵人會被施展者的召喚獸施予傷害增加的吸血蝙蝠吸血Debuff。
Effect: 技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#% x 2次{nl}一般召喚獸傷害增加 #{CaptionRatio}#%{nl}召喚惡魔召喚獸傷害增加 #{CaptionRatio2}#%{nl}{#339999}{ol}[吸血]{/}{/} 持續時間15秒
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Sorcerer14\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Sorcerer14\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]
Name: 吸血蝙蝠
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Name: 究極煉成
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (basicCoolDown < skill.MinCoolDown) {", "    return skill.MinCoolDown;", "}", "", "return basicCoolDown;"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}開設引出道具潛在性能的商店，可以使用隱藏屬性，但是道具的潛力會減少。
Effect: 每個武器都具有各自不同的潛在效果{nl}1級大師
Name: 道具覺醒
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Magic] - [Soul]{/}{/}{nl}聚集魔法能量後，向敵人發射並給予傷害。
Effect: 技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#% x 2次
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Alchemist9\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Alchemist9\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (basicCoolDown < skill.MinCoolDown) {", "    return skill.MinCoolDown;", "}", "", "return basicCoolDown;"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (basicCoolDown < skill.MinCoolDown) {", "    return skill.MinCoolDown;", "}", "", "return basicCoolDown;"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (basicCoolDown < skill.MinCoolDown) {", "    return skill.MinCoolDown;", "}", "", "return basicCoolDown;"]
Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Dark]{/}{/}{nl}把指定範圍內的敵人影子釘住，使其陷入無法行動的狀態。
Effect: 持續時間 #{CaptionTime}#秒

Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Onmyoji1\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Onmyoji1\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Dark]{/}{/}{nl}指示殭屍進行祭典。被殭屍碰到的敵人會受到傷害。殭屍們的平均力量屬性數值會以追加傷害套用。

Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Bokor18\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Bokor18\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Name: 避邪符
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Archer14\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Archer14\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = 15;", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill);", "return value;"]
Name: 跪射
SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Buff] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}寵物咆哮威脅敵人們。被施予咆哮的敵人會陷入無法行動狀態，對飛彈攻擊變得脆弱。(Boss怪物不會套用無法移動功能。){nl}寵物和主人的距離如果為 250以上，寵物的咆哮會停止。

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#993399}{ol}[Magic] - [Soul]{/}{/}{nl}讓本體移動至魂魄所在的地方，並在合體的位置上召喚攻擊敵人的魔法陣。只能在靈魂出竅使用。
Effect: 每1秒技能係數 #{SkillFactor}#%{nl}魔法陣持續時間 #{CaptionRatio}#秒
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var sklFactor;", "", "if (skillOwner.ClassName == 'PC') {", "    var atkType = skill.AttackType;", "    var attribute = skill.Attribute;", "    var atkTypebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, atkType);", "    var attributebyItem = GetSumOfEquipItem(skillOwner, attribute);", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel + atkTypebyItem + attributebyItem;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "} else {", "    sklFactor = skill.SklFactor + (skill.Level - 1) * skill.SklFactorByLevel;", "    return Math.floor(sklFactor);", "}", ""]
Name: 靈體合一
SP: ["function SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill) {", "    var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "    var decsp = 0;", "    var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "    if (basicSP == 0) {", "        return 0;", "    }", "", "    var lv = pc.Lv", "    bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "    if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "    } else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "        bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "    }", "", "    var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "    var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Magic] - [Soul]{/}{/}{nl}將魂魄往本體周圍分成好幾個，並同時引爆對敵人造成傷害。{nl}{#00113F}對受到天使之淚的攻擊的敵人， 會發動相當於衰弱傷害 30%的神聖屬性追加打擊。{/}

Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Sadhu25\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Sadhu25\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Holy]{/}{/}{nl}發動靈氣，提升自身周圍同伴們的HP恢復力。{nl}{#00113F}如果在守護性的Buff中，恢復力會增加 10%。{/}
Effect: 每3秒治癒係數 #{CaptionRatio}#%{nl}靈氣持續時間 60秒
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Paladin25\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Paladin25\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = 107 + (skill.Level - 1) * 6.2", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return value"]
Name: 恢復

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#993399}{ol}[Buff] - [Magic] - [Holy]{/}{/}{nl}暫時讓自己和組隊成員的火、冰、電氣、毒、地屬性抵抗力增加，並讓該屬性攻擊的傷害減少。
Effect: 屬性傷害 #{CaptionRatio}#% 減少{nl}持續時間 #{CaptionTime}#秒
Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Paladin26\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Paladin26\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = 10 + skill.Level * 2", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return value"]

Name: 鐵布衫
SP: ["var basicSP = skill.BasicSP;", "var decsp = 0;", "var bylvCorrect = 0", "", "if (basicSP == 0) {", "    return 0;", "}", "", "var lv = pc.Lv", "bylvCorrect = lv - 300", "", "if (bylvCorrect < 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 2.75 / 1000", "} else if (bylvCorrect >= 0) {", "    bylvCorrect = bylvCorrect * 1.25 / 1000", "}", "", "var value = basicSP * (1 + bylvCorrect)", "var abilAddSP = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "    decsp = value * zeminaSP", "}", "", "value = value - decsp;", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]
Description: {#DD5500}{ol}[Buff] - [Physical]{/}{/}{nl}用鍛練得很強的雙手採取可連續攻擊敵人的姿勢。基本攻擊套用為雙手攻擊。
Effect: 技能系數 #{SkillFactor}#% x 2次{nl}基本攻擊速度增加 #{CaptionRatio}#
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Monk12\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Monk12\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]

Attributes aren't supported yet;", "    abilAddSP = abilAddSP / 100;", "    value = Math.floor(value) + Math.floor(value * abilAddSP);", "    var zeminaSP = GetExProp(pc, \"ZEMINA_BUFF_SP\");", "", "    if (zeminaSP != 0) {", "        decsp = value * zeminaSP", "    }", "", "    value = value - decsp;", "", "    if (value < 1) {", "        value = 0", "    }", "", "", "    if (skill.ClassName == \"Scout_Cloaking\"  &&  IsBattleState(pc) == 1  &&  (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1  ||  IsPVPField(pc) == 1)) {", "        return 0", "    }", "", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "var value = SCR_Get_SpendSP(skill)", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'Wizard_Wild_buff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 1.5 * spRatio;", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'MalleusMaleficarum_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    value = value * 2", "    return Math.floor(value);", "}", "", "", "if (value < 1) {", "    value = 0", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'ShadowPool_Buff') == 'YES'  &&  skill.ClassName == \"Shadowmancer_ShadowPool\") {", "    value = 0;", "}", "", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Oracle_TwistOfFate\"  &&  GetZoneName(pc) == \"guild_agit_1\") {", "    return 0", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value);"]

CoolDown: ["var basicCoolDown = skill.BasicCoolDown;", "var abilAddCoolDown = 0 // @rjgtav. Attributes aren't supported yet;", "basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + abilAddCoolDown;", "", "if (skill.ClassName == \"Cleric_Heal\") {", "", "    if (IsPVPServer(pc) == 1) {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown + 28000", "    }", "", "}", "", "var laimaCoolTime = GetExProp(pc, \"LAIMA_BUFF_COOLDOWN\")", "", "if (laimaCoolTime != 0) {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * (1 - laimaCoolTime)", "} else if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'CarveLaima_Debuff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 1.2;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'GM_Cooldown_Buff') == 'YES') {", "    basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.9;", "}", "", "", "if (IsBuffApplied(pc, 'SpeForceFom_Buff') == 'YES') {", "", "    if (skill.ClassName != \"Centurion_SpecialForceFormation\") {", "        basicCoolDown = basicCoolDown * 0.5;", "    }", "", "}", "", "var ret = Math.floor(basicCoolDown) / 1000", "ret = Math.floor(ret) * 1000;", "return Math.floor(ret);"]

Effect_CaptionRatio: ["function SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill) {", "    var addAbilRate = 1;", "", "    if (\"Druid11\" != \"None\") {", "        var reinforceAbil = GetAbility(pc, \"Druid11\")", "", "        if (reinforceAbil != null) {", "            var abilLevel = TryGetProp(reinforceAbil, \"Level\")", "            var masterAddValue = 0", "", "            if (abilLevel == 100) {", "                masterAddValue = 0.1", "            }", "", "            addAbilRate = 1 + (reinforceAbil.Level * 0.005 + masterAddValue);", "        }", "", "    }", "", "    return addAbilRate", "}", "", "var value = skill.Level * 7", "value = value * SCR_REINFORCEABILITY_TOOLTIP(skill)", "return value"]

Description: {#993399}{ol}[Magic] - [Poison]{/}{/}{nl}在指定的位置上暫時長出長草。進入該地區的怪物暫時被判定為植物型怪物，陷入草毒Debuff狀態，受到持續傷害。進入該地區的我軍獲得花香Buff恢復HP。{nl}{#00113F}澤米娜女神像Buff活化中時，花香Buff的 HP 恢復量增加10%。{/}
Effect: 技能系數 #{SkillFactor}#%{nl}花香治癒系數 #{CaptionRatio}#%{nl}魔法陣持續時間 #{CaptionTime}#秒{nl}{#339999}{ol}[草毒]{/}{/} 持續時間 #{CaptionRatio2}#秒
Effect_SkillFactor: ["var value = skill.SklFactor + skill.SklFactorByLevel * (skill.Level - 1)", "var abil = GetAbility(pc, \"Druid15\")", "", "if (abil != null  &&  \"Druid15\" != 'None') {", "    var abilLevel = TryGetProp(abil, \"Level\")", "    var masterAddValue = 0", "", "    if (abilLevel == 100) {", "        masterAddValue = 0.1", "    }", "", "    var value = value * (1 + ((abilLevel * 0.005) + masterAddValue))", "    return Math.floor(value)", "}", "", "return Math.floor(value)"]
